  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare results of Intravascular Ultrasound (which occurs during cardiac catheterization)
      with Computed Tomography (CT) scan to detect blockages or narrowing of the arteries that feed
      the heart. These will be studied in the cardiac transplant population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
